    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1286">
<l>kāṇuṅkāṟ kāṇēṉ tavaṟāya kāṇākkāṟ </l>
<l>kāṇēṉ tavaṟalla vai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I see my husband, I do not see any faults; but when I do not see him, I do not see anything but faults.</l>
            </lg>
